---
layout: page
permalink: /projects
title: Projects
sub_title: I love developing software, and I'm always building and sharing stuff.
current_projects:
  title: Current
  sub_title: I'm trying to spend as much time as possible on these.
other_projects:
  title: More stuff
  sub_title: I also spend a lot of time building little projects to learn new stuff, here are just a few examples.
github_link:
  url: https://github.com/perezperret
  text: More on github
---

<div class="mx-auto container">
  <div class="py-12 container">
    <div class="max-w-xl">
      <h2 class="text-4xl heading"><%= page[:current_projects][:title] %></h2>
      <h2 class="text-xl mb-16 font-sans"><%= page[:current_projects][:sub_title] %></h2>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap -mx-12">
      <% site.data[:projects].select { _1[:current] }.each do |project| %>
        <div class="px-12 w-full md:w-1/2 mb-8">
          <%= partial 'projects/project', locals: { project: project } %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="py-12 container">
    <div class="max-w-xl">
      <h2 class="text-4xl heading"><%= page[:other_projects][:title] %></h2>
      <h2 class="text-xl mb-16 font-sans"><%= page[:other_projects][:sub_title] %></h2>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap -mx-12">
      <% site.data[:projects].select { !_1[:current] }.each.each do |project| %>
        <div class="px-12 w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 mb-8">
          <%= partial 'projects/project', locals: { project: project } %>
        </div>
      <% end %>

      <div class="px-12 w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 mb-8">
        <a href="<%= page[:github_link][:url] %>" target="_blank" class="block">
          <h3 class="text-2xl border-blue-400 heading heading--highlight">
            <%= page[:github_link][:text] %>
          </h3>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
